{"id":"api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat","title":"getLocaleNumberFormat","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat\", \"name\": \"getLocaleNumberFormat\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/i18n/locale_data_api.ts#L433-L472\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"getlocalenumberformat\">getLocaleNumberFormat<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat#getlocalenumberformat\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"50odwzlmi3es6h6ug3vjs0foj\">檢索給定語言環境下的數字格式。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat\" class=\"code-anchor\">getLocaleNumberFormat</a></span>(locale: string, type: <a href=\"api/common/NumberFormatStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">NumberFormatStyle</a>): string</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6cuhpqqkoxc2njmr3u8ccohar\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>locale</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9zj2ramyg5z8bjgrpbh20ttf4\">用於要使用的語言環境格式規則的語言環境程式碼。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7zgytlpr676in397zep1nxg0l\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>type</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/common/NumberFormatStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">NumberFormatStyle</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cejfv8jto7vbvl93fraqsug1r\">要格式化的數值型別（比如 <code>Decimal</code> 或 <code>Currency</code>）。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8u0py96ml87hjxfl85je8i1su\">本地化的格式字串。</p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/NumberFormatStyle\"><code>NumberFormatStyle</code></a></li>\n    <li><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"caj0wtt8v1nsf2ab2qiqc2q43\"><a href=\"http://cldr.unicode.org/translation/number-patterns\">CLDR 官網</a></p></li>\n    <li><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aksrl9bq7pw2jp42e7u98l906\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-overview\">國際化（i18n）指南</a></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2t7qasih7mjkhkjw6h58qlgtw\">以下是數字模式中使用的特殊字元：</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"59oyga6lqqizmnssov9ehkre\"><em>重要：</em><code>.</code> <code>,</code> <code>0</code>\n<code>#</code>（以及以下的）字元是特殊的佔位符，它們代表數字分隔符等，而不是真實的字元。你絕不能『翻譯』這些佔位符。例如，不要把\n<code>.</code> 修改成\n<code>,</code>，雖然在你的語言中小數點分隔符是寫成逗號的。該符號會被其本地化等價物替換，也就是適合你的語言的\n<code><a href=\"api/common/NumberSymbol\" class=\"code-anchor\">NumberSymbol</a></code>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8zm4yarznh5dvv4v4n1k47yoh\">以下是數字模式中使用的特殊字元：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5xiw1gbpmrz9czmn84a7vngz\">符號</th>\n<th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6ryq83o4vnwnm29aax9uihwua\">含義</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>.</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"24c5tof8vsy9hs6csjjherux9\">自動替換為用作小數點的字元。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>,</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dukee8b6db2kqzq4btbk558dk\">替換為（千）『分組』分隔符。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>0</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"10hejp0fgw7rtnb4amch734ob\">替換為一個數字（如果沒有足夠的數字，則為零）。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>#</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"65ayectq4mmvjb5mde1jsufyd\">用數字代替（如果數字不足，則不進行任何替換）。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>¤</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8afpz0gsqgawp3isa0n2k10v9\">替換為貨幣符號，比如 $ 或 USD。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aoof9wdtwoz0akfbrcunoi5dy\">標記百分比格式。％符號可能會更改位置，但必須保留。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>E</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"asu3u8ntfzbtvr2xvlarbc1ys\">標記科學計數法格式。 E 符號可能會改變位置，但必須保留。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>'</td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9r7mg1ktb0q74bjzvema9w336\">表示文字字面量的特殊字元，用 ASCII 單引號引起來。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/NumberFormatStyle\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - /guide/i18n-overview\n - api/common\n - api/common/NumberFormatStyle\n - api/common/NumberSymbol\n - api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat#description\n - api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat#getlocalenumberformat\n - api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat#see-also\n - http://cldr.unicode.org/translation/number-patterns\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/i18n/locale_data_api.ts#L433-L472\n-->"}